OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,F"This year it will be disrupted." said
OL,7,FBrian McLister who is the President of
OL,8,FBallycastle Chamber of Commerce.
OL,10,F"Over the weekend, there can be up to
OL,11,F250,000 people coming here.
OL,13,F"On a daily basis, it's between 70,000
OL,14,Fand 80,000 and they come from all
OL,15,Fparts of Ireland and Scotland to meet
OL,16,Ftheir friends that they haven't seen
OL,17,Fsince last year.
