OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FWhilst locals expect a similar number
OL,7,Fof visitors this year, there are
OL,8,Fexpected to be a smaller number of
OL,9,Flicensed stall holders this year in
OL,10,Fthe town centre.
OL,12,FFigures obtained by UTV show 142
OL,13,Fstreet trading licenses were issued
OL,14,Flast year by Causeway Coast and Glens
OL,15,FBorough Council.
OL,17,FThat is compared to just 109 this year.
