OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FLast year, some street traders
OL,7,Fcomplained that the opening hours of
OL,8,Fthe fair were curtailed - however, the
OL,9,Fcouncil assured UTV that the hours
OL,10,Fhave been extended following
OL,11,Fengagement with traders.
OL,13,FThe Council also said it was
OL,14,F"satisfied that the number of licences
OL,15,Fissued reflects the number issued in
OL,16,Frecent years" and that it had engaged
OL,17,Fwith local businesses and residents
OL,18,Fduring a recent information session.
