OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FBusiness owners in the seaside town
OL,7,Fare remaining positive about the
OL,8,Fprospect of the fair.
OL,10,F"It is one of the main economic
OL,11,Fdrivers that all the businesses in
OL,12,FBallycastle from the seafront up to
OL,13,FCastle Street look forward to, to put
OL,14,Fmoney in the banks to see you through
OL,15,Fthe lean months of November and
OL,16,FJanuary - it's fairly grim sometimes,"
OL,17,Fexplained Aidan Boyle who runs Boyle's
OL,18,FSpar on the seafront.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
