OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FWhilst dulse and yellowman remain
OL,7,Fstaples of the fair, the shopping
OL,8,Fhabits of fairgoers has also changed
OL,9,Fover the years.
OL,11,F"It's a very challenging environment,"
OL,12,FAidan said.
OL,14,F"People look at the Lammas Fair and
OL,15,Fthink, I remember this and that, but
OL,16,Fthose stall holders are not there any
OL,17,Fmore.
OL,19,F"Everything you can buy on a stall...
OL,20,Fthose things are all available online
OL,21,Fnow," he added.
