OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FThere are also changes to some other
OL,7,Fparts of the fair with this years'
OL,8,Famusements now being located on a
OL,9,Fsmaller, privately owned site nearer
OL,10,Fthe seafront instead of the
OL,11,Ftraditional site on the Quay Road
OL,12,FPlaying Fields where building works
OL,13,Fare taking place.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
