OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FThere are also fears that the
OL,7,Famusements will be smaller this year
OL,8,Fdue to the lack of a site at the Quay
OL,9,FRoad Playing Fields. "Council made
OL,10,Farrangements for an alternative site
OL,11,Fand advertised. There were no
OL,12,Fsubmissions from amusement providers,"
OL,13,Fa council spokesperson told UTV.
