OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,FThere was also controversy locally
OL,7,Fafter the line dancers who perform on
OL,8,Fthe seafront in the town were not
OL,9,Fallowed to perform in their normal
OL,10,Flocation. However, the council told
OL,11,FUTV that after engagement with the
OL,12,Fgroup, alternative provision had been
OL,13,Fprovided at the seafront.
OL,15,F"Over the years, additional
OL,16,Flegislation has made things just that
OL,17,Flittle bit more difficult," local Sinn
OL,18,FFein councillor Cara McShane told UTV.
