OL,3,CThe Lammas Fair - Ballycastle
OL,4,Cinstitution changing with time
OL,6,F"Although we like to be nostalgic and
OL,7,Flook back on yester-year, we do have
OL,8,Fto move with the times and road
OL,9,Fclosure orders, health and safety -
OL,10,Fall of these issues - but trying to
OL,11,Fensure that the Lammas Fair has that
OL,12,Frelaxed ethos," she said.
OL,14,F"You're going to see thousands of
OL,15,Fpeople from the top end of Ballycastle
OL,16,Fright to the seafront throughout the
OL,17,Fdays of the Lammas Fair."
